aldurs-gate-3-character-spotify-playlists-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/baldurs-gate-3-character-spotify-playlists-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/baldurs-gate-3-character-spotify-playlists-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/baldurs-gate-3-character-spotify-playlists-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/baldurs-gate-iii"><em>《博德之门 3》</em></a>演员 Samantha Béart 和 Neil Newbon 整理了 Spotify 播放列表，反映了他们各自的角色。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/best-upcoming-games-we-saw-at-gamescom-2023-3505950">以下是我们在 Gamescom 2023 上看到的一些即将推出的最佳游戏</a></strong></li></ul><p>以下是<em>《博德之门 3》</em>的剧透。</p><p>在游戏中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-fans-raise-hundreds-of-dollars-in-karlach-inspired-fundraiser-3502013">贝阿特扮演卡拉赫</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-actors-urges-fans-to-petition-for-more-dungeons-dragons-3506015">纽本扮演阿斯塔里昂</a>，这两个角色因其个性和庞大的故事情节赢得了大批粉丝。 </p><figure id="attachment_3502023" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3502023" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3502023" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/karlach-fundraiser.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/karlach-fundraiser.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/karlach-fundraiser-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/karlach-fundraiser-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/karlach-fundraiser-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/karlach-fundraiser-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/karlach-fundraiser-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3502023" class="wp-caption-text"> 《博德之门 3》图片来源：Larian Studios</figcaption></figure><p>由于她的心脏被地狱引擎取代，卡拉赫正在慢慢死去。尽管如此，她仍然富有同情心、幽默风趣，并为那些需要帮助或处境不利的人提供强烈的保护。</p><p>另一方面，阿斯塔里奥一开始就具有操纵性和自私性，对于坚持良好阵营的玩家来说很难让他喜欢自己的角色。然而，据透露，他原本是一位吸血鬼领主的奴隶，吸血鬼领主想要杀死他来提升。</p><p> Karlach、Astarion 和<em>《博德之门 3》</em>的其他角色是<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/baldurs-gate-3-review-3481761"><em>NME</em>游戏五星级评论</a>中的众多亮点之一，现在 Béart 和 Newbon 分享了让他们想起自己角色的歌曲播放列表。</p><p>在<a href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/4SANjT7whL2t6YsSxiAGQn?si=160607027f6c4a84&amp;nd=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Karlach 的播放列表</a>中，摇滚贯穿始终，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂斯</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jay-z">Jay-Z</a>的《Crazy In Love》、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bjork">比约克</a>的《Army Of Me》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cardi-b">Cardi B</a>的《Bodak Yellow》和卡罗尔·金的《You&#39;ve》 Got A Friend 穿插了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nine-inch-nails">九寸钉</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/motorhead">Motörhead</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/led-zeppelin">Led Zeppelin</a>的经典曲目。 </p><figure id="attachment_3478283" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3478283" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3478283" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-mod-for-multiclassing-on-easiest-difficulty.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-mod-for-multiclassing-on-easiest-difficulty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-mod-for-multiclassing-on-easiest-difficulty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-mod-for-multiclassing-on-easiest-difficulty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-mod-for-multiclassing-on-easiest-difficulty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-mod-for-multiclassing-on-easiest-difficulty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-mod-for-multiclassing-on-easiest-difficulty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3478283" class="wp-caption-text"> 《博德之门 3》图片来源：Larian Studios</figcaption></figure><p> Béart 在<a href="https://twitter.com/SamanthaBeart/status/1711526923518595263" target="_blank" rel="noopener">X 的帖子</a>中表示，播放列表背后的想法是这些歌曲是 Karlach 可以在卡拉 OK 上唱的。</p><p>根据<a href="https://gizmodo.com.au/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3s-astarion-talks-dd-acting-and-yes-bear-sex/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Gizmodo</em></a>的采访，Newbon 的<a href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/5M8V2xx6uPA5dMUhLU6Ij5?si=EbeL7NE8RRuu7S3QIgT8fg&amp;utm_source=copy-link&amp;utm_medium=copy-link&amp;nd=1&amp;_branch_match_id=1187723968906510579&amp;_branch_referrer=H4sIAAAAAAAAA8soKSkottLXLy7IL8lMq9TLyczL1k%2F1zyjI9LIMDXROAgCGVrBlIAAAAA%3D%3D" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Astarion 播放列表</a>有超过 130 首歌曲，用于“引导 [他] 进入角色动作，并在卷中的会话之前设定基调和氛围”。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-bowie">大卫·鲍伊 (David Bowie)</a>经常出现在现场，同时也收录了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-doors">The Doors</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rem">REM</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nirvana">Nirvana</a>的精选曲目。<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/barbie">芭比</a></em>原声带中<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lady-gaga">Lady Gaga</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ariana-grande">Ariana Grande</a>的《Rain On Me》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/doja-cat">Doja Cat</a>的《Paint The Town Red》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a>的《Dance The Night》也出现了，据说是为了配合阿斯塔里奥轻松愉快的一面。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，索尼终于展示了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/new-ps5-model-launches-in-november-with-a-detachable-disc-drive-3512906">PS5 的新型号，该型号</a>具有更纤薄的设计和可拆卸的光驱。</p><p>帖子<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gat