https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2023_bombaybicycleclub_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2023_bombaybicycleclub_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2023_bombaybicycleclub_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2023_bombaybicycleclub_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/bombay-bicycle-club">孟买自行车俱乐部 (Bombay Bicycle Club)</a>分享了由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chaka-khan">Chaka Khan</a>主演的新单曲《铁拳 2》，并宣布将在英国和爱尔兰进行巡演。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/bombay-bicycle-club-interview-my-big-day-3501961">孟买自行车俱乐部：“试图安全行事是没有意义的”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌是继专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bombay-bicycle-club-announce-new-album-my-big-day-share-title-track-3455992">主打歌</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bombay-bicycle-club-share-new-single-turn-the-world-on-and-announce-four-intimate-acoustic-shows-3498078">《Turn The World On》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/holly-humberstone">Holly Humberstone</a>合作的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bombay-bicycle-club-and-holly-humberstone-team-up-on-diving-3471153">《Diving》</a>和朦胧单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bombay-bicycle-club-share-hazy-new-single-i-want-to-be-your-only-pet-3487596">《I Want To Be Your Only Pet》</a>之后，他们即将发行的专辑《My Big Day》中的最后一首歌曲。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bombay-bicycle-club-share-hazy-new-single-i-want-to-be-your-only-pet-3487596">&#39;</a> 。您可以在下面收听并观看今晚英国夏令时下午 6 点首播的视频。</p><p> “这是一次相当疯狂的旅程，从坐在沙发上摆弄键盘和鼓机，到坐在洛杉矶一间豪华录音室里查卡·汗 (Chaka Khan) 对面给她唱歌指导，”主唱杰克·斯特德曼 (Jack Steadman) 说道。</p><p> “查卡绝对是一位超级巨星，整个体验非常积极。我认为这首歌反映了这一点——团结在一起，抛开任何不好的想法，享受这一刻。” </p><p><iframe title="Spotify Embed：《铁拳 2》（壮举。Chaka Khan）" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="352" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="au